@host = https://localhost:5001
@version = 1

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/health

###

### Registro de novo usuário (colaborador)
POST {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "João Colaborador",
  "email": "joao.colaborador@empresa.com",
  "password": "SenhaForte@123",
  "role": "Collaborator"
}

###

### Registro de novo usuário (gestor)
POST {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Maria Gestora",
  "email": "maria.gestora@empresa.com",
  "password": "SenhaForte@123",
  "role": "Manager"
}

###

### Login (colaborador) - pega o token e substitui abaixo
POST {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.colaborador@empresa.com",
  "password": "SenhaForte@123"
}

###

### Login (gestor) - pega o token e substitui abaixo
POST {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.gestora@empresa.com",
  "password": "SenhaForte@123"
}

###

# Cole aqui o token JWT do colaborador
@collabToken = REPLACE_WITH_COLLABORATOR_TOKEN

# Cole aqui o token JWT do gestor
@managerToken = REPLACE_WITH_MANAGER_TOKEN

###

### Dados do usuário logado (perfil) - colaborador
GET {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{collabToken}}

###

### Criar autoavaliação (colaborador)
POST {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/selfassessments
Authorization: Bearer {{collabToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": 4,
  "stress": 3,
  "workload": 4,
  "notes": "Semana corrida, mas controlada."
}

###

### Listar minhas autoavaliações (paginação + HATEOAS)
GET {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/selfassessments/my?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{collabToken}}

###

### Recomendações de IA para o colaborador logado
GET {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/ai/recommendations/me
Authorization: Bearer {{collabToken}}

###

### Criar evento de bem-estar (IoT / Mobile)
POST {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/wellnessevents
Authorization: Bearer {{collabToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": null,
  "eventType": "break",
  "occurredAt": null,
  "source": "mobile_app",
  "value": 15,
  "metadataJson": "{ \"description\": \"Pausa de 15 minutos\" }"
}

###

### Listar eventos de bem-estar (gestor) com paginação + filtros
GET {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/wellnessevents?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&eventType=break
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

###

### Dashboard anônimo para gestor (últimos 30 dias)
GET {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/dashboard/summary?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

###

### Relatório mensal de IA (gestor)
GET {{host}}/api/v{{version}}/ai/monthly-report?year=2025&month=3
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
